The '''seismic driver''' was the primary weapon of the [[Seismic tank/Legends|seismic tank]], a mining vehicle built by [[Haor Chall Engineering/Legends|Haor Chall Engineering]] that was repurposed for planetary assaults by the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|CIS]]. It consisted mainly of a gargantuan metal piston that would extend rapidly from the underside of the vehicle, generating colossal seismic shockwaves upon impact with the ground.

